  "detailed_description": "PaintballX is an online multiplayer FPS paintball game!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCurrent Features!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Weapon Pickups: pickup better weapons around the map for a competitive advantage against your opponents.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Sliding: slide around the map quickly for better positioning.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Game modes: Free for all and Team Deathmatch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Paintball Maps: Play on our paintball maps inspired from real paintball fields!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Scoreboard: Compete with your friends to see who can get the most kills!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAND MORE!",
